            <lg xml:id="TK1291">
<l>avarneñ cavarkkātal kaṇṭu mevaṉeñcē </l>
<l> nīyemak kākā tatu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my soul! although you have seen how his soul stands by him, how is it you do not stand by me?</l>
